==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Hindustani]] [[तन्दूर]] / {{URchar|[[تندور]]}} < Persian {{FAchar|[[تنور]]}} < Arabic {{ARchar|[[تنور|تَنُّور]]}}, all meaning [[oven]].
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''tandoor'''
# a [[cylindrical]] [[clay]] [[oven]] used, in [[South Asian]] [[cuisine]], to make flat [[bread]], or to bake [[meat]]

